### Chat with History
POST {{AIAgent.Host_HostAddress}}/ContosoTravelAgent/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hi, I am Sarah. I love beach vacations and water sports"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Hello Sarah! It's great to meet you. I'd be happy to help you plan a beach vacation with water sports activities. To provide you with the best recommendations, could you tell me:\n\n1. What type of water sports are you most interested in? (e.g., surfing, snorkeling, diving, jet skiing, parasailing)\n2. What's your preferred travel timeframe?\n3. Do you have a budget range in mind?\n4. Are you looking for a domestic or international destination?\n\nThis will help me suggest the perfect beach destination for your adventure!"
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I love snorkeling and diving. Looking to travel in March for about a week. Budget around $3000-4000"
    }
  ]
}

